trans-unit.source: The exception that is thrown when the specified token request (RST) is not understood because of an unknown token type.
trans-unit.target: Unntaket oppstod under den angitte token forespørselen (første) ikke er forstått på grunn av en ukjent token type.

trans-unit.source: The RST is represented by a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestSecurityToken> object.
trans-unit.target: FØRSTE representeres av en <xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestSecurityToken>objektet.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestSecurityToken>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.UnsupportedTokenTypeBadRequestException"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.UnsupportedTokenTypeBadRequestException"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: This constructor initializes the <xref:System.Exception.Message%2A> property of the new instance to a system-supplied message that describes the error.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren initialiserer den <xref:System.Exception.Message%2A>for den nye forekomsten til en system-angitt melding som beskriver problemet.</xref:System.Exception.Message%2A>

trans-unit.source: This message takes into account the current system culture.
trans-unit.target: Meldingen tar hensyn til den gjeldende kulturen i systemet.

trans-unit.source: The following table shows the initial property values for the new instance.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser første egenskapsverdiene for den nye forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: |Property|Value| |--------------|-----------| |<xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>|`null`.| |<xref:System.Exception.Message%2A>|The localized error message string.| |<xref:System.IdentityModel.UnsupportedTokenTypeBadRequestException.TokenType%2A>|An empty string.|
trans-unit.target: | Egenskapen | Verdien | |--------------|-----------| | <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>| `null`.| | <xref:System.Exception.Message%2A>| Lokaliserte feil melding strengen. | | <xref:System.IdentityModel.UnsupportedTokenTypeBadRequestException.TokenType%2A>| En tom streng. |</xref:System.IdentityModel.UnsupportedTokenTypeBadRequestException.TokenType%2A> </xref:System.Exception.Message%2A> </xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>

trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.UnsupportedTokenTypeBadRequestException"> </xref> klassen med den angitte tokentypen.

trans-unit.source: This constructor initializes the TokenType property to the specified token type URI and the <xref:System.Exception.Message%2A> property of the new instance to a system-supplied message that describes the error.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren initialiserer TokenType-egenskapen til den angitte tokentypen URI og <xref:System.Exception.Message%2A>for den nye forekomsten til en system-angitt melding som beskriver problemet.</xref:System.Exception.Message%2A>

trans-unit.source: This message takes into account the current system culture.

trans-unit.source: |Property|Value| |--------------|-----------| |<xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>|`null`.| |<xref:System.Exception.Message%2A>|The localized error message string.| |<xref:System.IdentityModel.UnsupportedTokenTypeBadRequestException.TokenType%2A>|The specified token type URI.|
trans-unit.target: | Egenskapen | Verdien | |--------------|-----------| | <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>| `null`.| | <xref:System.Exception.Message%2A>| Lokaliserte feil melding strengen. | | <xref:System.IdentityModel.UnsupportedTokenTypeBadRequestException.TokenType%2A>| Den angitte tokentypen URI. |</xref:System.IdentityModel.UnsupportedTokenTypeBadRequestException.TokenType%2A> </xref:System.Exception.Message%2A> </xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the token type URI.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder tokentypen URI.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.UnsupportedTokenTypeBadRequestException"></xref> class with serialized data.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.UnsupportedTokenTypeBadRequestException"> </xref> klasse serialiserte dataene.

trans-unit.source: This constructor is called during deserialization to reconstitute the exception object transmitted over a stream.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren kalles under deserialisering til reconstitute unntak objektet overføres via en dataflyt.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> object that holds the serialized object data.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> objekt som har datatypen serialiserte objektet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext> object that contains the contextual information about the source or destination.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>objekt som inneholder kontekstavhengig informasjon om kilden eller målet.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.UnsupportedTokenTypeBadRequestException"></xref> class with a specified error message and a reference to the inner exception that is the cause of this exception.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.UnsupportedTokenTypeBadRequestException"> </xref> klassen med en angitt feilmelding og en referanse til det interne unntaket er årsaken til dette unntaket.

trans-unit.source: An exception that is thrown as a direct result of a previous exception should include a reference to the previous exception in the <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Et unntak som er registrert som en direkte resultatet av et tidligere unntak må inkludere en referanse til det tidligere unntaket i den <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property returns the same value that is passed into the constructor.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>egenskapen returnerer den samme verdien som er sendt til konstruktøren.</xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>

trans-unit.source: The following table shows the initial property values for the new instance.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser første egenskapsverdiene for den nye forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: |Property|Value| |--------------|-----------| |<xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>|The inner exception reference.| |<xref:System.Exception.Message%2A>|The error message string.| |<xref:System.IdentityModel.UnsupportedTokenTypeBadRequestException.TokenType%2A>|`null`.|
trans-unit.target: | Egenskapen | Verdien | |--------------|-----------| | <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>| Referansen for det indre unntaket. | | <xref:System.Exception.Message%2A>| Feil melding strengen. | | <xref:System.IdentityModel.UnsupportedTokenTypeBadRequestException.TokenType%2A>| `null`.|</xref:System.IdentityModel.UnsupportedTokenTypeBadRequestException.TokenType%2A></xref:System.Exception.Message%2A></xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>

trans-unit.source: The error message that explains the reason for the exception.
trans-unit.target: Feilmelding som forklarer hvorfor unntaket.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Exception> that is the cause of the current exception.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Exception>som er årsaken til den gjeldende unntaket.</xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: If the `exception` parameter is not <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>, the current exception is raised in a <xref uid="langword_csharp_catch" name="catch" href=""></xref> block that handles the inner exception.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den `exception` -parameteren er ikke <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>, oppstår det gjeldende unntaket i en <xref uid="langword_csharp_catch" name="catch" href=""> </xref> blokken som behandler det interne unntaket.

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> object with the unsupported token type and other exception information.
trans-unit.target: Angir den <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> objekt med andre informasjon om unntak og tokentypen støttes ikke.

trans-unit.source: GetObjectData sets a <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo> with all the exception object data targeted for serialization.
trans-unit.target: GetObjectData angir en <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>med alle objektet unntaksdataene mål for serialisering.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>

trans-unit.source: During deserialization, the exception object is reconstituted from the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo> transmitted over the stream.
trans-unit.target: Under deserialisering, reconstituted unntak-objektet fra den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>overføres via dataflyten.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>
